comments: Hield (SAC) makes contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) arm during the driving shot attempt affecting his ability to finish at the rim.
Bagley III (SAC) establishes a legal position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic (DAL) on-ball.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) arm during his drive.
Hield (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Doncic (DAL).
Barnes (SAC) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) and Fox (SAC) make incidental contact as they engage during the loose ball.
Hield (SAC) makes incidental contact with Powell's (DAL) arm during the jump ball.
Hield (SAC) makes incidental contact with Doncic's (DAL) hand on the ball as he contests the driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) moves laterally into Fox's (SAC) path during the drive and affects his SQBR.
Kleber (DAL) makes incidental contact with Bjelica (SAC) after the release on his shot attempt near the rim.
Hield (SAC) briefly grasps Hardaway Jr. (DAL) before releasing during the inbound.
Replay review of the foul called on Bjelica (SAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Curry (DAL).
